歩:["止: stop; footprint (RTK)　少: few","walk","WALK, step","When<strong> walk</strong>ing your pet, you must <em>stop </em>a<em> few</em> times along the way when nature calls.","When you learn to<strong> walk</strong>, you take your <em>steps</em> a <em>few</em> at a time. Picture a clumsy but happy toddler who falls every <em>few</em> <em>steps</em> but keeps getting up to try again.","ホ、 ブ、 フ","ある.く、 あゆ.む","歩 【ホ】 step, stride, counter for steps<br>歩道 【ホドウ】 footpath, walkway, sidewalk<br>徒歩 【トホ】 walking, going on foot<br>譲歩 【ジョウホ】 concession, conciliation, compromise<br>歩 【ブ】 unit of land measurement, 3.95 square yards, 3.31 square metres (meters)<br>歩留り 【ブドマリ】 yield, yield rate<br>町歩 【チョウブ】 hectare (2.471 acres)<br>町段畝歩 【チョウタンセブ】 units of square measure (for rice fields, forests, etc.)<br>歩 【フ】 pawn<br>歩兵 【フヒョウ】 pawn<br>敵歩 【テキフ】 opponents pawn","歩く 【あるく】 to walk<br>歩む 【あゆむ】 to walk, to go on foot"],
