歴:["厂: cliff　林: grove; forest　止: stop; footprint (RTK)","curriculum","PERSONAL HISTORY","A<strong> CURRICULUM</strong> is a <em>calendar</em> that replaces days with reasons to <em>stop</em> having fun.","A<strong> curriculum</strong> (vitae) is similar to a <em>calendar</em> except that, instead of mentioning every <em>day</em> in your life, it only mentions the main <em>stop</em>s. (Compare <a href=\"/study/kanji/%E6%9A%A6\">暦</a> (<span class=\"frnr\">#226</span>)).","レキ、 レッキ","","歴 【レキ】 history of, experience of<br>歴史 【レキシ】 history<br>経歴 【ケイレキ】 personal history, career<br>学歴 【ガクレキ】 academic background<br>歴とした 【レッキトシタ】 accepted, fully-fledged, clear, respectable",""],
