義:["羊: sheep　我: ego","righteousness","RIGHTEOUSNESS　MEANING, sense　SUBSTITUTE, artificial","Righteous Christians are sheep with egos (reworked from raulir, fixes word order to match radical order).","Follow the path of<strong> RIGHTEOUSNESS</strong> like <em>sheep</em> follow the shepherd , let go of your <em>ego</em>.","ギ","","義 【ギ】 morality, righteousness, justice, honour (honor), meaning, teachings, doctrine, nonconsanguineous relationship (i.e. of in-laws), prosthesis<br>義務 【ギム】 duty, obligation, responsibility<br>講義 【コウギ】 lecture<br>主義 【シュギ】 doctrine, rule, principle",""],
議:["言: word; say　義: righteousness","deliberation","DISCUSS　LEGISLATIVE BODY","Careful<strong> deliberation</strong> produces <em>words</em> of <em>righteousness</em>.","Picture Samuel L Jackson's character in Pulp Fiction carefully deliberating over what words to say to freak someone out before killing them. He even browses through a list of bible quotations for inspiration. Then he finds it!... \"the path of the righteous man\".","ギ","","議 【ギ】 discussion, deliberation, thought, opinion<br>議論 【ギロン】 argument, discussion, dispute, controversy<br>会議 【カイギ】 meeting, conference, session, assembly, council, convention, congress<br>不思議 【フシギ】 wonder, miracle, strange, mystery, marvel, curiosity",""],
犠:["牛: cow (⺧)　義: righteousness","sacrifice","SACRIFICE","A cow that is righteous<strong> sacrifice</strong>s her milk for the human race.","<em>Cows</em> are truly <em>righteous</em> animals. They<strong> SACRIFICE</strong> their milk so that we can have some. And if they don't have any left, they give a <em>sheep</em> a <em>hand fiesta</em> (good lord this is going too far) and give us that instead. What <em>righteous</em> <em>cows</em>.","ギ、 キ","いけにえ","犠牲 【ギセイ】 victim, sacrifice, scapegoat<br>犠牲者 【ギセイシャ】 victim<br>供犠 【クギ】 sacrifice, sacrificial animal",""],
