貧:["分: part; segment　貝: shellfish; money, clam (RTK)","poverty","POOR","In the case of true<strong> poverty</strong>, not having money is only part of the problem. There are other components as well, like lack of education, class structuring, etc., but that doesn't really matter. Just remember that the money is only part of it, not the whole.","Parting with your money will lead to<strong> poverty</strong>.","ヒン、 ビン","まず.しい","貧 【ヒン】 poverty, becoming poor, living in poverty<br>貧困 【ヒンコン】 poor, needy, lacking, meagre, meager<br>赤貧 【セキヒン】 extreme poverty<br>清貧 【セイヒン】 honourable poverty, honorable poverty<br>貧 【ヒン】 poverty, becoming poor, living in poverty<br>貧乏 【ビンボウ】 poverty, destitute, poor","貧しい 【まずしい】 poor, needy, lacking (quantity and quality-wise), poor, scanty, skimpy, slight, inadequate<br>貧しい家 【まずしいいえ】 poor family"],
