軸:["車: car　由: reason; sprout (RTK); shoot (RTK)","axis","AXLE　AXIS","An absurd image, but what the heck - worked for me. Imagine a <em>car</em> going across a plain at a fast speed. Suddenly a single <em>sprout</em> (the only one to be seen) gets stuck to the car's wheels, causing the car to fly around its<strong> axis</strong>.","The Germans manufactured so many <em>cars</em> during World War II that it was almost as if they were <em>sprouting</em> from the factories of the<strong> Axis</strong>.","ジク","","軸 【ジク】 axis, stem, shaft, axle, center, focal point, key point<br>軸足 【ジクアシ】 pivot leg<br>車軸 【シャジク】 axle<br>地軸 【チジク】 earth's axis",""],
