挟:["手: hand; fingers (扌) (RTK)　夾: scissors","sandwiched","HOLD BETWEEN, pinch","挟まる 【はさまる】 (v5r,vi) to get between; to be caught in; (P) Story: You know how in tokyo there are those really packed trains where train staff in gloves shove people in? Well imagine being<strong> sandwiched</strong> in so tight, that when the doors close, only your FINGERS are sticking out. The train staff have no choice... they must cut them off with SCISSORS =( snip snip..","Fingers<strong> sandwiched</strong> between a pair of scissors. Don't move or else!","キョウ、 ショウ","はさ.む、 はさ.まる、 わきばさ.む、 さしはさ.む","挟撃 【キョウゲキ】 pincer movement, pincer attack<br>挟殺 【キョウサツ】 rundown","挟む 【はさむ】 to interpose, to hold between, to insert, to be on either side (e.g. road), to be across (e.g. street, river), to be beyond<br>挟まる 【はさまる】 to get between, to be caught in<br>差し挟む 【さしはさむ】 to insert, to interrupt, to slip in a word, to harbor (e.g. doubts), to harbour, to entertain (e.g. a theory)"],
