繕:["糸: thread; Spider-Man (RTK)　善: virtuous","darning","MEND","After a day being <em>virtuouos</em> and keeping the city safe, <em>Spiderman</em>'s outfit is in need of some repair. Luckily, as he can shoot out threads<strong> darning</strong> is very easy for him to do.","<strong>Darning</strong> is too obscure a word for me, I prefer to just think of it as repair. And obviously, repairing someones broken cloth things is a virtuous thing to do, and you need thread to do it.","ゼン","つくろ.う","修繕 【シュウゼン】 repair, mending<br>営繕 【エイゼン】 upkeep (of equip.)","繕う 【つくろう】 to mend, to patch up, to repair, to fix, to darn, to trim, to fix (hair, clothes, appearance etc.), to adjust, to tidy up, to groom, to keep up appearances, to cover up (mistakes etc.), to gloss over, to treat (illness, injury, etc.)"],
