経:["糸: thread; Spider-Man (RTK)　圣: holy; spool (RTK)","sūtra","PASS THROUGH, longitude　MANAGE　SUTRA, scripture","The word ‘sutra’ literally means a rope or thread that holds things together. Here we see that it is a <em>spool</em> that is holding the <em>threads</em> together.","Suggestion: Replace \"spool\" with \"toilet paper/roll\". Reasons: (1) <em>Toilet paper/roll</em> usually comes on a <em>spool</em>. (2) <em>Toilet paper</em> is used to clean the <em>soil</em> off your <em>crotch</em>. Story: <em>Spiderman</em> (= thread) has a roll of <em>toilet paper</em> with the words of a<strong> sutra</strong> printed on each sheet (picture <em>Spiderman</em> saying the<strong> sutra</strong> as he tears sheets off the <em>toilet roll</em>). Spool also appears in <a href=\"/study/kanji/%E8%8C%8E\">茎</a> (<span class=\"frnr\">#772</span>), <a href=\"/study/kanji/%E6%80%AA\">怪</a> (<span class=\"frnr\">#773</span>), <a href=\"/study/kanji/%E8%BB%BD\">軽</a> (<span class=\"frnr\">#774</span>), <a href=\"/study/kanji/%E5%BE%84\">径</a> (<span class=\"frnr\">#947</span>).","ケイ、 キョウ","へ.る、 た.つ、 たていと、 はか.る、 のり","経 【ケイ】 warp (weaving), longitude, scripture, sutra, trans-<br>経済 【ケイザイ】 economics, business, finance, economy<br>神経 【シンケイ】 nerve, nerves, sensitivity<br>直径 【チョッケイ】 diameter<br>経 【キョウ】 sutra, Buddhist scriptures<br>経典 【キョウテン】 sacred books, sutras, scriptures, Bible<br>説経 【セッキョウ】 lecture on the sutras<br>法華経 【ホケキョウ】 Lotus Sutra","経る 【へる】 to pass, to elapse, to go by, to pass through, to go through, to experience, to go through, to undergo<br>経つ 【たつ】 to pass, to lapse<br>経糸 【たていと】 (weaving) warp"],
紳:["糸: thread; Spider-Man (RTK)　申: monkey (RTK)","sire","GENTLEMAN","Monkeys are very adept at swinging around trees. But when they met Spiderman, who could swing around even better than they could, they all quickly addressed him as<strong> sire</strong>.","You are now two-thirds of the way through the book! Keep it up!","シン","","紳士 【シンシ】 gentleman<br>紳士的 【シンシテキ】 gentlemanly<br>貴紳 【キシン】 noble, men of rank, notables<br>縉紳 【シンシン】 person of rank, person of status, ranked official",""],
