勤:["堇: cabbage, scarecrow (RTK)　力: power; strength; muscles (RTK)","diligence","SERVICE, work, employment","Growing <em>cabbages</em> takes <em>muscle</em> and<strong> diligence</strong>.","With enough <strong>diligence</strong>, Koreans can turn ordinary <em>cabbage</em> into <em>powerful</em> kimchi.","キン、 ゴン","つと.める、 -づと.め、 つと.まる、 いそ.しむ","勤勉 【キンベン】 diligent, industrious<br>勤務 【キンム】 service, duty, work<br>通勤 【ツウキン】 commuting to work<br>出勤 【シュッキン】 attendance (at work), being at work, presence (in the office), going to work, reporting for work<br>勤行 【ゴンギョウ】 religious service<br>勤行時報係 【ゴンギョウジホウガカリ】 muezzin","勤める 【つとめる】 to work (for), to be employed (at), to serve (in), to serve (as), to act (as), to fill (the position of), to play the role (of), to conduct a religious service<br>勤まる 【つとまる】 to be fit for, to be equal to, to function properly<br>勤しむ 【いそしむ】 to endeavor, to endeavour, to work hard (at)"],
漢:["水: water (氵) (氺)　堇: cabbage, scarecrow (RTK)","Sino-","(ancient) CHINESE; Han dynasty　FELLOW, man","In the <em>water</em> between Japan and China, the<strong> Sino-</strong> side has put <em>scarecrows</em> in the water to try and keep the Japanese away.","Take the left to be \"kanji\" not scarecrow.<strong> Sino-</strong> (Chinese) people had to put a lot of sweat into learning the kanji. See the drops of sweat coming off.","カン","","漢 【カン】 China, Han (majority Chinese ethnic group), man<br>漢字 【カンジ】 Chinese characters, kanji<br>痴漢 【チカン】 masher, molester, pervert<br>暴漢 【ボウカン】 hoodlum, ruffian",""],
嘆:["口: mouth　堇: cabbage, scarecrow (RTK)","sigh","SIGH, lament","A <strong>sigh</strong> escapes the <em>mouth</em> of the <em>scarecrow</em>, who laments: \"...if I only had a brain, I could learn kanji\".","I will let out a huge<strong> sigh</strong> of relief from my mouth when I learn the last kanji.","タン","なげ.く、 なげ.かわしい","嘆 【タン】 sigh, grief, lamentation<br>嘆願 【タンガン】 entreaty, appeal, petition<br>感嘆 【カンタン】 admiration, wonder, astonishment<br>悲嘆 【ヒタン】 grief, sorrow, anguish, lamentation","嘆く 【なげく】 to sigh, to lament, to grieve<br>嘆かわしい 【なげかわしい】 sad, wretched, deplorable<br>嘆かわしい事態 【なげかわしいじたい】 deplorable situation"],
