閲:["門: gate　兑: devil (RTK) (兌)","review","REVIEW, inspect","A little <em>devil</em> at the <em>gates of hell</em><strong> review</strong>s your record to see if you're evil enough to get in.","As I was <strong>reviewing</strong> for my exam at a quiet saloon, the <em>devil</em> popped out of nowhere and offered to make sure I pass. But I told him no way, since that's cheating. Besides, I'm just <strong>reviewing</strong> things I already know. I won't fail. But he kept insisting, so I kicked him and sent him crashing through the entrance <em>gates</em>.","エツ","けみ.する","閲 【エツ】 inspection (esp. of a document), stamp of approval (for a document)<br>閲覧 【エツラン】 inspection, reading, browsing (the WWW, Internet), web browsing<br>検閲 【ケンエツ】 censorship, inspection, examination, to censor, to inspect (in order to censor), to review (in order to censor)<br>校閲 【コウエツ】 revision, proofreading","閲する 【えっする】 to inspect, to examine, to check, to elapse, to pass (time)"],
