晩:["日: day; sun　免: dismiss; rabbit (RTK)","nightfall","EVENING","At<strong> nightfall</strong> the <em>sun excuses</em> itself and goes to sleep.","This is EASY!!! Japanese people see a RABBIT ON THE MOON (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moon_rabbit ) and so<strong> nightfall</strong> is when the <em>sun</em> leaves to make way for the <em>rabbit</em>.","バン","","晩 【バン】 evening, counter for nights<br>晩御飯 【バンゴハン】 dinner, evening meal<br>毎晩 【マイバン】 every night<br>今晩 【コンバン】 tonight, this evening",""],
