些:["此: this; current; next; coming; last; past　二: two","whit","A LITTLE BIT","Those two tourists from my tour group don't have a<strong> whit</strong> of common sense. They never <em>stop and sit down</em> when the tour guide tells them to!","<em>Two</em>-year-olds don't have a<strong> whit</strong> of interest to <em>stop and sit down</em>. They'd likely explode with all that energy.","サ、 シャ","ち.と、 ち.っと、 いささか","些細 【ササイ】 trivial, slight<br>些事 【サジ】 something small or petty, trifle<br>些々 【ササ】 trifling, trivial","些と 【ちっと】 a little bit, a little while<br>些と 【ちっと】 a little bit, a little while<br>些とも 【ちっとも】 not at all (neg. verb)<br>聊か 【いささか】 a little, a bit, somewhat"],
