髭:["髟: long  hair　此: this; current; next; coming; last; past","beard","BEARD, mustache","\"Please <em>stop and sit down</em> to look to the painting up there\", the tour guide says. \"We don't know exactly who is on the painting, but from the <em>shape</em> of the <em>hair</em> and the distinctive <em>beard</em>, we think they meant to depict President Lincoln.\"","A<strong> beard</strong> is hair that, instead of wanting it SHAPED like your friends, you grow it LONG so that you can STOP, SIT DOWN and scratch it thoughtful while considering this here and that there.","シ","ひげ、 くちひげ","","髭 【ひげ】 moustache, beard, whiskers, extremely short pulse appearing on an electrical signal<br>髭剃り 【ひげそり】 shaving, shaver<br>顎髭 【あごひげ】 beard (esp. on the chin), goatee<br>口髭 【くちひげ】 moustache, mustache"],
