啄:["","peck at","","Just like the ones on a rhinoceros, there are little birds who like to<strong> peck at</strong> the skin near the <em>mouth</em> of a <em>sow</em> and clean it.","The typical story of <em>anorexia nervosa</em>: a pitiful emaciated girl who doesn't really eat, but rather just <strong>PECK</strong>s <strong>AT</strong> her food, keeping her <em>MOUTH</em> as tiny as a sparrow's beak, all the while thinking of herself as a gigantic <em>SOW</em>. [thx CharleyGarrett].","タク、 ツク、 トク","ついば.む、 つつ.く","啄木 【タクボク】 woodpecker<br>啄木鳥 【キツツキ】 woodpecker","啄む 【ついばむ】 to pick at, to peck at"],
吠:["口: mouth　犬: dog","barking","HOWL, bark","The <em>mouth</em> of a <em>chihuahua</em> is good at<strong> barking</strong>.","The smaller the MOUTH the bigger the<strong> barking</strong> hence the fact the chihuaha is damn annoying.....","ハイ、 ベイ","ほえ.る、 ほ.える","吠瑠璃 【ベイルリ】 beryl","吠える 【ほえる】 to bark, to bay, to howl, to bellow, to roar, to cry<br>吠える 【ほえる】 to bark, to bay, to howl, to bellow, to roar, to cry"],
