坦:["","flat","","I'm usually<strong> flat</strong> on the <em>soil</em> passed out at <em>nightbreak</em>.","I have a nice big garden with one problem – moles! Anyway, when I get up at <em>nightbreak</em> (= dawn) there are always piles of <em>soil</em> (molehills) everywhere. My first task of the day is to jump on them to make them<strong> flat</strong>.","タン","たいら","坦懐 【タンカイ】 level emotion, frankness<br>坦坦 【タンタン】 level, peaceful<br>平坦 【ヘイタン】 even, flat, level<br>亜富汗斯坦 【アフガニスタン】 Afghanistan",""],
