惟:["","ponder","","The <em>state of mind</em> of a <em>turkey</em> is to<strong> ponder</strong> the meaning of life while waiting to be eaten come November.","Brain: \"I'm in a lucid <em>state of mind</em>. Pinky, are you<strong> ponder</strong>ing what I'm<strong> ponder</strong>ing?\" Pinky: \"Yes Brain, but how are we going to get the <em>turkey</em> up here?\"","イ、 ユイ","おも.んみる、 これ、 おも.うに","思惟 【シイ】 thought, thinking, speculation, using wisdom to get to the bottom of things, focusing one's mind, deep contemplation, concentrating, deliberating, pondering, reflecting<br>思惟 【シイ】 thought, thinking, speculation, using wisdom to get to the bottom of things, focusing one's mind, deep contemplation, concentrating, deliberating, pondering, reflecting","思い見る 【おもいみる】 to reflect carefully<br>此れ 【これ】 this (indicating an item near the speaker, the action of the speaker, or the current topic), this person (usu. indicating someone in one's in-group), now, here, I (me), certainly<br>思うに 【おもうに】 presumably, conceivably, in my opinion, in my view, I think (that), upon thought, upon reflection"],
惚:["心: heart; mind (忄; ⺗)　忽: in a moment; instantly; all of a sudden; neglect; disregard","infatuation","FALL IN LOVE WITH; grow senile","<strong>Infatuation</strong> is the <em>state of mind</em> that makes a <em>knot</em> form in your <em>heart</em>.","<strong>Infatuation</strong> is the <em>state of mind</em> when you <em><a href=\"/study/kanji/%E5%BF%BD\">忽</a> (<span class=\"frnr\">#2431</span>)</em> fall in love.","コツ","ほけ.る、 ぼ.ける、 ほ.れる","恍惚 【コウコツ】 ecstasy, trance","呆ける 【ぼける】 to grow senile, to be childish with age, to be mentally slow, to be befuddled, to play stupid, to say something stupid (oft. on purpose; esp. as part of a comedic routine), to become engrossed (in something)<br>惚れる 【ほれる】 to fall in love, to be in love, to be charmed with, to lose one's heart to"],
怜:["","quickwitted","","The commando team under <em>orders</em> need to be<strong> quickwitted</strong> and are always in the right <em>state of mind</em> for action.","Data, orders: Commander <em>Data</em> is as<strong> quickwitted</strong> as they come. While Picard is still in the process of uttering an <em>order</em>, <em>Data</em> is already executing it!","レイ、 レン、 リョウ","あわ.れむ、 さと.い","伶俐 【レイリ】 cleverness, sagacity<br>怜悧狡猾 【レイリコウカツ】 cunning, crafty, shrewd, guileful",""],
惇:["","considerate","","The <em>state of mind</em> of the <em>tall child</em> whom <em>receives</em> all of the attention is often surprisingly<strong> considerate</strong>. They have known nothing but kindness in their life, and thus act the same in return!","A<strong> considerate</strong> <em>state of mind</em> is open to <em>receive</em> others' input.","シュン、 ジュン、 トン","あつ.い","敦厚 【トンコウ】 sincerity and kindheartedness, honesty and simplicity<br>敦朴 【トンボク】 honest and homely, simple",""],
恰:["","as if","","I was in a <em>state of mind</em> to ask my wife if some slinky outfit from the closet <em>fit</em> her. \"<strong>As if</strong>!\" she yelled, \"that belonged to your previous girlfriend!\"","My husband and I often have the same <em>state of mind</em>. We believe that's why we <em>fit together</em> well,<strong> as if</strong> we are meant for each other.","コウ、 カッ、 チョウ、 キョウ","あたか.も","格好 【カッコウ】 shape, form, figure, posture, pose, appearance, state, situation, suitable, fit, reasonable, about<br>格好つける 【カッコウツケル】 to affect a stylish air, to try to look good, to show off<br>丁度 【チョウド】 just, right, exactly","恰も 【あたかも】 as if, as it were, as though, right then, just then, at that moment<br>恰も好し 【あたかもよし】 luckily, fortunately"],
恢:["","enlarge","","Imagine the <em>state of mind</em> of a person who takes some viagra, thinking it will<strong> enlarge</strong> his package, but somehow it reduces it to <em>ashes</em> instead.","He was in a terrible <em>state of mind</em> when his home that he was <strong>enlarging</strong> was consumed by a fire and everything he had build up was turned to <em>ashes</em>.","カイ、 ケ","ひろ.い","回復 【カイフク】 restoration, rehabilitation, recovery, return, replevin, improvement, recovery (from an illness), recuperation, convalescence<br>天網恢々 【テンモウカイカイ】 heaven's vengeance is slow but sure, heaven's net is wide and coarse, yet nothing slips through",""],
悌:["","respect for elders","","The <em>state of mind</em> of a <em>younger brother</em> has<strong> respect for elders</strong>, including you if you're the elder brother.","Data, younger brother: Commander <em>Data</em> had a <em>younger, amoral brother</em> (Lore). When they visited an old computer museum, Lore remarked that he could compute much faster than the machines on exhibition. That's when Data found it to be his duty to teach his brother <strong>respect for elders</strong>.","テイ、 ダイ","","悌 【テイ】 respect for one's elders, harmony among siblings<br>悌順 【テイジュン】 obedience<br>孝弟 【コウテイ】 filial piety, brotherly love",""],
