湊:["","port","","They started <em>playing music</em> when the ship of the emperor came in sight over the <em>water</em> and was brought into<strong> port</strong>.","Across the WATER we could hear the band PLAYing MUSIC, actually \"Anchors Aweigh,\" as our ship left<strong> PORT</strong>.","ソウ","みなと、 あつ.まる","輻輳 【フクソウ】 congestion (e.g. traffic), overcrowding, convergence (esp. optical)","港 【みなと】 harbour, harbor, port<br>春の湊 【はるのみなと】 end of spring"],
淋:["","solitude","","Picture yourself living in<strong> solitude</strong> on a tiny island. There are only <em>two trees</em>, and you keep getting splashed by <em>water</em> from sea waves.","Tom Hanks in Castaway living in<strong> solitude</strong> on an island surrounded by <em>water</em> with just two <em>trees</em> (a grove) for a hammock. (thanks Katsuo).","リン","さび.しい、 さみ.しい","【リンパ】 lymph<br>淋菌 【リンキン】 gonococcus (Neisseria gonorrhoeae)<br>味醂 【ミリン】 mirin, type of sweet rice wine used in cooking","寂しい 【さびしい】 lonely, lonesome, solitary, desolate<br>寂しい 【さびしい】 lonely, lonesome, solitary, desolate"],
