芙:["","lotus flower","","[+woelpad] In a certain culture, there is a ritual carried out when a girl is quite young (young enough, in fact, that they do it before they are considered a woman in that culture - for the same reason that some cultures do not name a baby until they are sure it will live) - she must go on a vision quest for a<strong> lotus flower</strong> and look inside it to see the face of her <em>husband</em> - then report back.. Imagine a poor flower girl's dismay when she looks into the<strong> lotus flower</strong> and sees the face of <em>Homer Simpson!</em>","There's a popular myth amongst <em>flower</em> girls that the face of their future <em>husband</em> is hidden inside a<strong> lotus flower</strong>.","フ","","芙蓉 【フヨウ】 cotton rose (Hibiscus mutabilis), Confederate rose, dixie rosemallow, lotus blossom<br>芙蓉峰 【フヨウホウ】 Mount Fuji, Mt. Fuji",""],
