芹:["","parsley","","The <em>axe</em> murderer glares at his <em>flower</em> garden victims \"First<strong> Parsley</strong>, Sage, Rosemary, and Thyme!\"","Cooking for Cannibals: Sprinkling a freshly chopped<strong> parsley</strong> <em>flower</em> onto your <em>axe</em> before cutting up those helpless victims is a great way to add a little zest to your dishes.","キン","せり","","芹 【せり】 Java water dropwort (Oenanthe javanica), Japanese parsley<br>セリ科 【セリか】 Apiaceae, parsley family of plants"],
苫:["","thatching","","The<strong> thatching</strong> of the old thatched roofs in rural Japan often has FLOWERS growing out of it when it's gotten weathered. So you can pluck them and use them like tea leaves to tell your FORTUNE.","The <em>fortuneteller</em> wants the<strong> thatching</strong> of his roof done with <em>flowers</em> instead of reeds.","セン","とま","","苫 【とま】 woven mat (of sedge, hay, etc.)"],
蒼:["","pale blue","","The <em>godown</em> was filled with<strong> pale blue</strong> <em>flowers</em>, probably some drug...","If you give her<strong> pale blue</strong> <em>flowers</em>, she'll <em>godown</em> on you every time.","ソウ","あお.い","蒼鉛 【ソウエン】 bismuth<br>蒼海 【ソウカイ】 blue waters<br>欝蒼 【ウッソウ】 thick, dense, luxuriant","青い 【あおい】 blue, green, pale, unripe, inexperienced"],
藁:["","straw","","When a giant drinks a cocktail, he needs a<strong> straw</strong> of large proportions. He hollows out a <em>tall</em> <em>tree</em> for the<strong> straw</strong>, and sticks a giant <em>flower</em> on the rim of his drink.","Story of three little pigs. First one built a house out of<strong> straw</strong> but it got blown down. Second one built a house out of <em>flowers</em> but it got blown down. Third one built a <em>tall</em> house out of <em>wood</em>. It was so tall, when the wolf blew it it fell back on the wolf, killing him instantly. The end.","コウ","わら","","藁 【わら】 straw<br>藁紙 【わらがみ】 straw paper, rice paper<br>麦わら 【むぎわら】 wheat straw, barley straw<br>敷き藁 【しきわら】 (animal's) litter"],
