柊:["","holly","","The<strong> holly</strong> <em>tree</em> has leaves which are always green. This is very practical in <em>winter</em>, when so much isn't, so that's why it became very popular as christmas decoration.","The<strong> holly</strong> is a <em>tree</em> that lasts through <em>winter</em> (aka the \"<strong>holly</strong> days\") (thanks herman).","シュ、 シュウ","ひいらぎ","","柊 【ひいらぎ】 holly olive (Osmanthus heterophyllus), false holly, holly, spotnape ponyfish (Leiognathus nuchalis)<br>柊菜 【ひいらぎな】 mizuna (Brassica rapa var. nipposinica)<br>西洋柊 【せいようひいらぎ】 English holly (Ilex aquifolium)"],
柚:["","citron","","The<strong> citron</strong> is relatively unknown overseas, but<strong> citron</strong> <em>trees</em> are beginning to <em>sprout</em> up everwhere in Japan.","In keeping with the move to greener autos Citroën has introduced its new line which instead of 油 <a href=\"/study/kanji/%E6%B2%B9\">油</a> (<span class=\"frnr\">#1107</span>) runs on an extract from<strong> citron</strong> <em>trees</em>.","ユ、 ユウ、 ジク","ゆず","柚 【ユズ】 yuzu (species of aromatic Asiatic citron, Citrus junos)<br>柚香菊 【ユウガギク】 Japanese aster (Kalimeris pinnatifida), false aster<br>晩白柚 【バンペイユ】 Citrus grandis, Citrus maxima<br>柚 【ユズ】 yuzu (species of aromatic Asiatic citron, Citrus junos)<br>柚香菊 【ユウガギク】 Japanese aster (Kalimeris pinnatifida), false aster","柚 【ゆず】 yuzu (species of aromatic Asiatic citron, Citrus junos)<br>柚子胡椒 【ゆずこしょう】 condiment paste made from yuzu zest and chili peppers (chile)"],
