枇:["","loquat","","A<strong> loquat</strong> is a tropical fruit <em>tree</em>, that <em>compared</em> to other trees has an odd seasonal pattern: it's fruit is ripe in late winter or early spring.","The<strong> loquat</strong> tree is very rare. To<strong> loquat</strong>e it, you need to <em>compare</em> it to the <em>trees</em> next to it.","ビ、 ヒ","","枇杷 【ビワ】 loquat (Eriobotrya japonica), Japanese medlar<br>びわ酒 【ビワシュ】 loquat wine",""],
