栞:["","bookmark","","<em>Two</em> birds high up in a <em>tree</em> <em>drying</em> out after flying through a storm. \"How will we get back on track? We lost our bearings!\" number one cries. \"Don't worry,\" the other one says, as he flips out his mobile. \"I have it <strong>bookmarked</strong>.\"","I love to use dried leaves as<strong> bookmark</strong>s. Every time I go by a tree, I pluck off a couple of leaves and then dry them to later use as<strong> bookmark</strong>s.","カン","しおり","","栞 【しおり】 bookmark, guidebook"],
椰:["","coconut tree","","(Note: <em>ear</em> + <em>city walls</em> = <a href=\"/study/kanji/%E8%80%B6\">耶</a> (<span class=\"frnr\">#2720</span>)). I see a <em>tree</em> with an <em>exclamation</em> mark painted on it. \"Why is that?\" I think, \"An <em>exclamation</em> mark indicates danger, but it's only a <em>tree</em>\". Then a coconut drops on my head. Ah, it's a<strong> coconut tree</strong>.","A<strong> coconut tree</strong> drops a coconut on your head, causing you to make an obscene <a href=\"/study/kanji/%E8%80%B6\">耶</a> (<span class=\"frnr\">#2720</span>).","ヤ","やし","椰子 【ヤシ】 palm tree<br>椰胡 【ヤコ】 yehu (bowed Chinese instrument with a coconut-shell body)","椰子 【やし】 palm tree<br>ヤシ科 【ヤシか】 Palmae (palm family of plants), Arecaceae"],
