痰:["","phlegm","","When your <em>sickness</em> involves <em>inflammation</em>, you will produce<strong> phlegm</strong> (perhaps in<em>phlegm</em>ation?)","If I'm <em>sick</em>, and have an <em>inflammation</em> of my lungs, I cough up a lot of<strong> phlegm</strong>.","タン","","痰 【タン】 phlegm, sputum<br>痰唾 【タンツバ】 sputum, phlegm<br>血痰 【ケッタン】 bloody phlegm<br>喀痰 【カクタン】 expectoration, sputum",""],
