磯:["石: stone; rock (RTK)　幾: how many; abacus (RTK)","rocky beach","ROCKY BEACH","To qualify as a<strong> rocky beach</strong> (as opposed to a sandy beach), <em>how many stones</em> does the beach need?","\"<em>How many stones</em> can you find at a<strong> rocky beach</strong>?\" the Zen Master asked his baffled pupil.","キ","いそ","","磯 【いそ】 (rocky) beach, seashore<br>磯辺 【いそべ】 seashore, beach, food wrapped in nori<br>荒磯 【あらいそ】 reefy coast, windswept and wave-beaten shore"],
